{"tid":1104032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖慎入)警方發言人指毀容中學生「左面擦傷」","createTime":"2019-04-12T21:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T03:38:36.000Z","uid":126585,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"57319bb7e55b8a15ba52ed47e31c6ce7170e4ca0","tid":1104032,"uid":126585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"警方發言人則稱，事件牽涉一名16歲姓蔡的男學生以及一名17歲的菲裔男學生，當時兩人在校內更衣室發生推撞，姓蔡學生<span style=\"color: red;\">左面擦傷</span>，菲裔學生則臉部腫了。警方把案件暫列作<span style=\"color: red;\">普通襲擊案處理</span>，交灣仔CID第4隊調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OUDMjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OUDMjZ.png&h=456cd80f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsGbmTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsGbmTj.png&h=5eb2acf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190412/59480785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480785&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=bc163169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480785&h=668ffc89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190412/59480785</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比人界到咁都仲叫「擦傷」同列作普通襲擊案處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講仲以為個菲仔傷得仲嚴重過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"80642cfe26815ead19bdbb3673bf8339f315aabb","tid":1104032,"uid":246639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"